Namespace Dekuple.Model

Classes

ModelBase

Common for all Models. Models are created from a Registry, have an OnDestroyed event, and are persistent by default.

ModelRegistry

Default registry for models. Of course, you can create your own registry that is not based on Dekuple.Model.IModel.

This is useful as a starting point at least, and will probably serve well for most applications.

PositionedModelBase

Interfaces

ILocalScaledModel

Base for models which require a tracked scale in local space.

IModel

Base for all persistent models.

IModelRegistry

IPositionedModel

Base for models which require a tracked world position.

IRotatedModel

Base for models which require a tracked rotation.

ITransformModel

Base for models which require a fully tracked transform.

IWorldScaledModel

Base for models which require a tracked scale in world space.
